      "id": "PopularPost223756",
      "post_content": "@Toquinha, no, protection from red will absolutely save a creature from this, because even though it's not targeted, it's doing damage, which protection prevents regardless. People REALLY need to learn protection rules.  \n  \nA card with protection from X cannot be targeted, blocked, damaged, OR enchanted by anything with the characteristic of X.  \nStill the world's best target for Hallow.",
