    {
      "id": "PopularPost285388",
      "post_content": "I think that I haven't read \"multiplayer\" yet... In 4 or 5 player, it's so easy to pay only ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) to clean the battlefield! I want four! Cheaper than every other [Wrath of God](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God) version, not more effective but funnier and easier to abuse!  \n  \nIn a duel, after the first, your opponent can play around it and you have to pay about ![6](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=6&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) to destroy a couple of creatures... Not so great anymore! Good, but not extremely good... Better card can be the usual suspects: [Pyroclasm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm), [Slagstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slagstorm), [Volcanic Fallout](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Fallout), [Sulfurous Blast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sulfurous Blast) (yes, I think it's a good card...), and the new [Mizzium Mortars](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mizzium Mortars).  \n  \nI really like these kind of \"burn everything\" in red, it's the red kind of control! This one in particular is so hilarious! You deal 13 damages to a bounch of 2/2 or 3/3 creatures, more than enought to kill them 3 or 4 times... Talk about overkill!   \n  \n4/5",
      "posted_by": "leomistico",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost285388\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I think that I haven't read \"multiplayer\" yet... In 4 or 5 player, it's so easy to pay only <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> to clean the battlefield! I want four! Cheaper than every other <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wrath of God\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God\">Wrath of God</a> version, not more effective but funnier and easier to abuse!<br/><br/>In a duel, after the first, your opponent can play around it and you have to pay about <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"6\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=6&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> to destroy a couple of creatures... Not so great anymore! Good, but not extremely good... Better card can be the usual suspects: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pyroclasm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm\">Pyroclasm</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Slagstorm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slagstorm\">Slagstorm</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Volcanic Fallout\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Fallout\">Volcanic Fallout</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sulfurous Blast\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sulfurous Blast\">Sulfurous Blast</a> (yes, I think it's a good card...), and the new <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mizzium Mortars\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mizzium Mortars\">Mizzium Mortars</a>.<br/><br/>I really like these kind of \"burn everything\" in red, it's the red kind of control! This one in particular is so hilarious! You deal 13 damages to a bounch of 2/2 or 3/3 creatures, more than enought to kill them 3 or 4 times... Talk about overkill! <br/><br/>4/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '285388'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy822\">leomistico</span>\r\n                                (12/12/2012 3:20:18 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                